                                            </svg>
                                        </a>
                                    </div>
                                </article>

                                <article class="holding-news-card">
                                    <div class="holding-news-media"><img src="/holding_website/static/src/img/be47af712e534dec5ef1bc8e42ee46f74fe131a8.png" alt="News 3" class="holding-news-media-image"/></div>
                                    <div class="holding-news-body">
                                        <div>
                                            <p class="holding-news-date">12 March 2025</p>
                                            <p class="holding-news-text">Title Text Goes here Title Text Goes here</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <a href="/media-center" class="holding-outline-button" aria-label="Read more">
                                            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                                <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
                                            </svg>
                                        </a>
                                    </div>
                                </article>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="holding-content-section" id="history-section">
                        <div class="holding-section-shell">
                            <div class="holding-history-layout">
                                <div>
                                    <h2 class="holding-history-title">History of Success</h2>
                                    <p class="holding-copy-light">ABULJADYEL SKY Holding is the parent holding company of Abdullatif H. Abuljadayel &amp; Sons, serving as a strategic platform for managing and developing a diverse portfolio of companies across investment, real estate, industry, and technology.</p>

                                    <div class="holding-timeline">
                                        <div class="holding-timeline-line"></div>
                                        <div class="holding-timeline-list">
                                            <div class="holding-timeline-item">
                                                <span class="holding-timeline-year">1984</span>
                                                <div class="holding-timeline-logos">
                                                    <p class="holding-timeline-label">Founded</p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>

                                            <div class="holding-timeline-item">
                                                <span class="holding-timeline-year">2023</span>
                                                <div class="holding-timeline-logos">
                                                    <p class="holding-timeline-label">Founded</p>
                                                    <img src="/holding_website/static/src/img/d0d2b2b629a995e0f6539b48701978eae93a7ee4.png" alt="Cloud Systems Tech" class="holding-timeline-logo"/>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>

                                            <div class="holding-timeline-item">
                                                <span class="holding-timeline-year">2023</span>
                                                <div class="holding-timeline-logos">
                                                    <p class="holding-timeline-label">Founded</p>
                                                    <img src="/holding_website/static/src/img/b502299d4187931475eea934395209906bfd8008.png" alt="ALAJCHEM Factory" class="holding-timeline-logo"/>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>

                                            <div class="holding-timeline-item">
                                                <span class="holding-timeline-year">2025</span>
                                                <div class="holding-timeline-logos">
                                                    <p class="holding-timeline-label">Founded</p>
                                                    <img src="/holding_website/static/src/img/4b41496abc3bcd1a0cad60100024aa00da8f07b3.png" alt="Abuljadyel Sky Holding" class="holding-timeline-logo"/>
                                                    <img src="/holding_website/static/src/img/d32546a2c1f63b13c15d94e35cc97f0321afd97c.png" alt="Secure Growth" class="holding-timeline-logo"/>
                                                    <img src="/holding_website/static/src/img/d0d2b2b629a995e0f6539b48701978eae93a7ee4.png" alt="Cloud Systems Tech" class="holding-timeline-logo"/>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <a href="#history-section" class="holding-gradient-button" style="margin-top:32px;">Our History</a>
                                </div>

                                <div class="holding-history-images">
                                    <div class="holding-history-card is-back"><img src="/holding_website/static/src/img/ecf5657ac9798454ccaffddd5e90d76651ff2d65.png" alt="History" class="holding-history-card-image"/></div>
                                    <div class="holding-history-card is-front"><img src="/holding_website/static/src/img/22bad24c89ab08d6a2cf95b2a15df76a742e2b09.png" alt="History" class="holding-history-card-image"/></div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="holding-services-shell" id="services-section">
                        <div class="holding-section-shell">
                            <div class="holding-services-card">
                                <div class="holding-services-blob"></div>
                                <p class="holding-watermark holding-services-watermark">Our Services</p>
                                <div class="holding-section-shell" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
                                    <h2 class="holding-services-title">Our Services</h2>
                                    <p class="holding-services-copy">Established in 1984 single-handed by Sheik Abdullatif H. Abuljadayel It was started by acquiring worldwide known brands, HACH-For Water Quality and CHEMSEARCH -Industrial Maintenance Chemicals, and ever since then as per growing market demands for Water Sector in the Kingdom, more product line has been acquired as a comprehensive organization offering more products for Lab requirements</p>

                                    <div class="holding-services-grid">
                                        <div class="holding-service-item">
                                            <h3 class="holding-service-title">Cloud Systems</h3>
                                            <p class="holding-service-copy">Established in 1984 single-handed by Sheik Abdullatif H. Abuljadayel It was started by acquiring worldwide known brands,</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="holding-service-item">
                                            <h3 class="holding-service-title">Real-estate</h3>
                                            <p class="holding-service-copy">Established in 1984 single-handed by Sheik Abdullatif H. Abuljadayel It was started by acquiring worldwide known brands,</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="holding-service-item">
                                            <h3 class="holding-service-title">Laboratory Instruments</h3>
                                            <p class="holding-service-copy">Established in 1984 single-handed by Sheik Abdullatif H. Abuljadayel It was started by acquiring worldwide known brands,</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="holding-service-item">
                                            <h3 class="holding-service-title">Networks &amp; Information Security</h3>
                                            <p class="holding-service-copy">Established in 1984 single-handed by Sheik Abdullatif H. Abuljadayel It was started by acquiring worldwide known brands,</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="holding-service-item">
                                            <h3 class="holding-service-title">chemical manufacturing</h3>
                                            <p class="holding-service-copy">Established in 1984 single-handed by Sheik Abdullatif H. Abuljadayel It was started by acquiring worldwide known brands,</p>
